snippet.title: I am a Math Teacher _ Global Math Project
snippet.description: We at the GMP firmly believe that teachers are the best and most fabulous advocates of joyful, meaningful, uplifting, and inspiring mathematics. Some teachers from around the world took part in this video as we experiment on how best share the joy and pride of teaching mathematics with the world.  This is a first attempt and we welcome guidance and thoughts for next steps!
